[Reference
---------
Bowers JR, Valentine M, Harrison V, et al. Genomic analyses of acute flaccid myelitis cases among a cluster in Arizona provide further evidence of enterovirus D68 role. MBio. 2019; 10(1). pii: e02262-18; https://mbio.asm.org/content/10/1/e02262-18.long

The availability of a rapid and EV-D68 specific assay can be quite helpful, especially when early AFM cases are reported. Use of rapid tests during an outbreak investigation can help confirm or rule out this frequent cause of AFM. - Mod.UBA]
